#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:67
#: dcc2dfcde20a413eb01ca24208427624
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution for exposure (S→E)"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:`j' 节点:math:`i ' 传递接触的日志概率(S E)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:69
#: d1c12d0ab794413bb1ce774747dac05b
msgid ""
"m_{ji}^{(k)} = \\mathbf{1}\\!\\left(h_j^{(k-1)}=1 \\land "
"e_j^{(k-1)}=0\\right)\\,\\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)}=\\ mathbf{1}\\!}\\左(h j^{(k-1)}\\land e j^{(k-1)\\0\\右)\\,\\log(1-\\β)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:75
#: 6e4c53836cc840cc9a14c108da50f690
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its exposure probability"
msgstr "节点 : math:`i'收集所有邻居的贡献 : math:`N(i)'计算其暴露概率"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:77
#: 4cc41a1e27eb45ca9a55e492facc52e3
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr "m i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)} m {ji}^{(k)}\\右)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:82
#: b08ba297ed254c87a8ea9479975548b5
msgid ""
"The integer tensors and indicator variables are updated with independent "
"uniform random variables :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{exp}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, "
"U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\sim \\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`"
msgstr ""
"整数计数器和指标变量以独立的统一随机变量更新 : math : 'U i^{\\ mathrm{exp}}, U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}},"
" U i^{\\ mathrm{rec}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)'"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR_ct.rst:86
#: 741b3a9c7ee344338518ba56b2a21a4b
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"t_i^E &= k, \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{exp}}<m_i^{(k)}) \\land (h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land r_i^{(k-1)}=0) \\\\\n"
"t_i^I &= k, \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}<1-exp(-\\alpha \\cdot \\Delta t_i^E)) \\land e_i^{(k-1)}=1\n"
"\\end{aligned}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"t i^E &= k,\\text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{exp}}<m i^{(k)})\\land (h i^{(k-1)}=0\\land r i^{(k-1)}=0)\\\\.\n"
"t i^I \\ k,\\ text{if} (U i i mathrm{inf}}<1-exp(-\\ alpha\\cdot\\Delta t i^E))\\land e i^{(k-1)\\1)\\1\n"
"结束{对齐}"

